    {
      "key": "contribution.{CyberExpress1703d-kiha101aterazawa}.description",
      "source": "左沢線を走るキハ100系(キハ101形)です。トイレなし、オールロングシートの編成です。",
      "translation": "This is a Kiha 100 Series (Kiha 101 type) running on the Aterazawa Line. It is a formation without toilets and with all long seats."
